name: BabyWhisperer
0:
”Alexa open baby whisperer”
”why is my baby crying”

skdetail:
This skill contains: dynamic content.
Invocation Name: baby whisperer
des: This app tells you why your baby is crying, e.g. whether they are hungry, tired, or need a diaper change. It also suggests actions you can take. For instance, if the baby is tired, it asks you if you would like some white noise/lullabies to help baby sleep.
priv: The developer reported that this skill does not collect personal information.
